		public static string Field_TemperatureCurveInputVariable = @"This field sets the second independent variable in the three temperature dependent performance curves~ to the entering condenser water temperature. Manufacturers express the performance of their chillers typically using the entering condenser water temperature (from the tower). ). This alpha field contains the keyword for the type of temperature input variable, , either {EnteringCondenserTemperature}, or {LeavingCondenserTemperature}. The default is EnteringCondenserTemperature.";
