  0,                                     !- Coefficient 3 of the Part Load Performance Curve
  0,                                     !- Coefficient 4 of the Part Load Performance Curve
  0,                                     !- Minimum Flow Rate {m3/s}
  Intermittent;                          !- Pump Control Type


  Pump:VariableSpeed,
