  OutdoorAir:Mixer,        !- Outside Air Mixer Object Type
  TU1 OA Mixer,            !- Outside Air Mixer Object Name
  COIL:Cooling:DX:VariableRefrigerantFlow,  !- Cooling Coil Object Type
